.SS Geometry
.TP
\f[CR]hypot[x, y]\f[R]
Get the length of the length of the hypotenuse of a right angle triangle
with sides of length `x' and `y', from origin (0, 0).
.SS Special Functions
.TP
\f[CR]gamma[x]\f[R]
Perform the gamma of `x'.
.TP
\f[CR]lgamma[x]\f[R]
Perform the natural logarithm of the absolute gamma of `x'.
.TP
\f[CR]erf[x]\f[R]
Perform the value of the error function at `x'.
.TP
\f[CR]erfc[x]\f[R]
